{"tid":1898558,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【2020 財政預算案】民建聯望香港非永久性居民能受惠「派錢」","createTime":"2020-02-26T06:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T06:48:24.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"525852ebd271f2b1c55d6fe08b9a254fb968fbe5","tid":1898558,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"立法會議員陳恒鑌表示，「全民抗疫」應該包括幫助香港非永久性居民，認為他們深受疫情影響，故稍後會向政府爭取，令非永久性居民能受惠「派錢」，或是爭取成立關愛基金協助他們。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員陳克勤表示，若然財政預算案順利通過，市民有望於2021年4月底獲政府派發的一萬元，但若審議期間預算案遭到拉布等阻撓，則預計7月後才能開始派錢。他又建議政府抽出派錢方案，直接交由財委會獨立審議，方便通過，讓市民盡快獲得一萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1385778288289790&amp;id=176401029227528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1385778288289790%26id%3D176401029227528&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X3O%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=d581413c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1385778288289790&amp;id=176401029227528</a>"},{"pid":"2e0cb9893c21af69ed404335999adf34f5b4ef9b","tid":1898558,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:46:27.000Z","msg":"每日300條蟲"},{"pid":"8ace3e363c859e45791c23f7522ade9c0d317f47","tid":1898558,"uid":255637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"直接交由財委會獨立審議，方便通過 <br />\n<br />\n呢句岩"},{"pid":"9b6fbbdcd6d27ebd5e7e433490e5a4d3bca329b1","tid":1898558,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}